{
  "design_notes": "S0 (Intro) begins sparse, gently easing standard players in with smooth lane transfers and adjacent eighth-note pairs, completely avoiding any high-speed double-lane jumps. S1 (Drop/Build) introduces more syncopated rhythm profiles as the song transitions into a high-energy build, using clean zig-zag sequences. S2 (Main Drop) reaches peak density to match the energy curve, mapping low-band beats to the BAR lane and using adjacent outer lanes to highlight melodic pitches without physical strain. S3 (Outro) relaxes the intensity back to sparse quarter-note pacing, fading out smoothly with a final hold.",
  "sections": [
    {
      "name": "Intro",
      "start_bar": 0,
      "intent": "A gentle synth intro establishing the core beat. Keep density low with comfortable spacing."
    },
    {
      "name": "Drop Build",
      "start_bar": 5,
      "intent": "Energy ramps up. We introduce more frequent eighth notes mapped to adjacent lanes."
    },
    {
      "name": "Main Drop",
      "start_bar": 7,
      "intent": "Maximum energy. We use a syncopated zig-zag pattern mapping drums and synth accents dynamically."
    },
    {
      "name": "Outro",
      "start_bar": 13,
      "intent": "The music winds down. We transition to sparse quarter notes to let the player ride the wave home."
    }
  ],
